sub_topic: The self-similarity of the Mandelbrot set.
message_1: What is the fractal dimension of the boundary of the Mandelbrot set? Answer the question with a numerical value rounded to two decimal places.
message_2: The fractal dimension of the boundary of the Mandelbrot set is not known exactly. However, it is known to be greater than 1 and less than 2. Some numerical estimates suggest it is around 1.50, but there is no definitive answer.
